Market Opportunities:
•	Growing Applications in Energy Storage Solutions: With the rise of electric vehicles (EVs) and renewable energy systems, the demand for copper powder in battery electrodes and conductive coatings is expected to surge.
•	Technological Advancements in Powder Metallurgy: Innovations in powder metallurgy techniques are opening new avenues for copper powder in high-performance industrial applications.
•	Expansion of Smart Manufacturing & IoT: The integration of copper-based conductive materials in IoT-enabled devices is anticipated to create lucrative growth opportunities.
